link_name: Dell Compellent Storage Center SNMP template
link_desc:
Template for monitoring Dell Compellent Storage system over SNMP from Dell Compellent storage Center.

SNMP LLD for controllers, enclouseres, disks, volumes.

Device info, statuses, triggers for disks/volumes related problems.

Value mappings used for this template:

ScItemStatus

1- Up

2- Down

3 - Degraded

scServerCnctvy

1 - Up

2-Down

3-Parial

Dell Open Manage System Status

1-Other (undefined)

2-Unknown

3-Ok

4-NonCritical [warning]

5-Critical [failure]

6-NonRecoverable [dead]
